  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13108684/februaryhero-900x500.jpg" alt="FebruaryHero" data-udi="umb://media/7e754456165242a4839538861ddd8152" /></p>
<h2>Lapland in February</h2>
<p>Why go on holiday to Lapland in February? </p>
<ul>
<li>February is a great time to visit Lapland - you will find some fantastic <a data-udi="umb://document/5d43a74b744d46078ab904e3e1c68f60" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5d43a74b744d46078ab904e3e1c68f60}" title="Half Term">Half-term deals</a> when booking for this time of year. </li>
<li>February half-term is perfect for <a data-udi="umb://document/0016db267e7444d59b5a6b951eaaab3d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0016db267e7444d59b5a6b951eaaab3d}" title="Family holiday to Lapland">families</a></li>
<li>You can still try all the activities available from <a data-udi="umb://document/c2bd76aba5e94e7d95f0525095d2c4ec" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c2bd76aba5e94e7d95f0525095d2c4ec}" title="Husky Rides">Husky sleigh rides</a> to skiing as there is still great snow at this time of year. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/25851216a21f4fddaee986c799f732cd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25851216a21f4fddaee986c799f732cd}" title="Deals" class="c-btn">Lapland deals</a></p>
<p>Enjoy a range of fun excursions - Lapland offers everything from Husky sleigh rides, meeting reindeer, a days skiing to an overnight trip in a glass igloo. View all the available excursions: </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da}" class="c-btn">Lapland excursions</a></p>
<h3>Best resorts in Lapland during February </h3>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Levi</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13108781/levifebruary-900x500.jpg" alt="LeviFebruary" data-udi="umb://media/5d341ecb716543738f302a5062c1da27" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Immerse yourself in the local culture and traditions of Lapland and enjoy local Sami talks or interesting museums. </li>
<li>If you are an animal lover, then it is worth making the most of all the <a data-udi="umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da}" title="Lapland Excursions">excursions</a> Levi has to offer, including Husky or Reindeer sleigh rides. </li>
<li>Try out the <a data-udi="umb://document/008434ab1df94295a36a19d2f43a10b8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/008434ab1df94295a36a19d2f43a10b8}" title="Cuisine of Finland">local cuisine of Lapland</a> at many of their traditional restaurants that can be found in resort.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi" class="c-btn">View Levi resort</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Yllas</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13108689/yllasfebruary-500x330.jpg" alt="YllasFebruary" data-udi="umb://media/f2e332ba8d3341f9baa0377a28708de4" /></p>
<ul>
<li>A skier or not, it is still worth making a trip on the Gondola to enjoy the amazing views (and café) from the top. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas" class="c-btn">View Yllas resort</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Saariselka</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13108687/saariselkafebruary-500x330.jpg" alt="SaariselkaFebruary" data-udi="umb://media/6f24210b97c149d7be94020ee70c077c" /></p>
<ul>
<li>The resort is the gateway to Urho Kekkonen National Park - find lots of information on this park at the Panorama Theatre.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka" class="c-btn">View Saariselka resort</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<h3>Best Lapland accommodation in February</h3>
<p>Here we have selected a highlighted accommodation option per the above resorts to give you an overview of the range of accommodation options you will will find available in Lapland.</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Levi Hotel Spa</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi"><strong>Levi</strong></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13107262/levi_hotel_spa_levi_reception-900x500.jpg" alt="LeviHotelSpa" data-udi="umb://media/d490c4eddb3942d8b70a8192818c26d0" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Offering a range of family friendly facilities including the popular Water World swimming zone. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/90d811ea285b4ddeb1c54c1384a7e3ec" href="/{localLink:umb://document/90d811ea285b4ddeb1c54c1384a7e3ec}" title="Levi Hotel Spa" class="c-btn">View Levi Hotel Spa</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Kuukkeli Log Cabins</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka"><strong>Saariselka</strong></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13099806/saariselka-cabin-1.jpg" alt="LogCabins" data-udi="umb://media/25e2f3bd57944827b6dc2167605ea1c4" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Situated in a convenient location in resort, the cosy cabin will make you feel at home. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/88ab24140f494052864fd3b80baa80e4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/88ab24140f494052864fd3b80baa80e4}" title="Kuukkeli Log Cabins" class="c-btn">View Kuukkeli Log Cabins</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Yllas Saaga Hotel</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas"><strong>Yllas</strong></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13080112/lapland-hotel-saaga-3.jpg" alt="YllasSaaga" data-udi="umb://media/843980670cef455d858f61a865ec3c89" /></p>
<ul>
<li>A modern, resort hotel with excellent spa facilities - perfect for any type of holiday maker. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/3afff877d41a4e3db0dd313844ee3446" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3afff877d41a4e3db0dd313844ee3446}" title="Yllas Saaga Spa Hotel" class="c-btn">View Yllas Saaga</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Santa Breaks holidays</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13078531/shutterstock_157220045.jpg" alt="SantaBreaks" data-udi="umb://media/a77c001d78a74a3593c0fc359d0d7fc3" /></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a}" title="Santa Breaks" class="c-btn" data-="">View Santa breaks holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to book your holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Travel, accommodation and transfers? We’ve got you covered. Book your holiday online or give us a call. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
